    m_HorizontalOverflow: 0
    m_VerticalOverflow: 0
    m_LineSpacing: 1
  m_Text: "You are in debt. The machine is your only way out.\n\nSet your bet and
    spin the reels.\nMatch all three symbols to win.\n\nMatching two symbols won\u2019t
    save you \u2014\nbut it may give you something useful.\n\nUse items to influence
    the game, but choose wisely.\nYou can only use two items each round.\n\nReach
    2000 points to escape."
